"{\"uid\": \"news.cgtn.com-news-2024-07-25-B-Girl-Liu-Qingyi-wants-to-show-Chinese-style-at-2024-Olympic-Games-1vwhPzJbIZO-p.html\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Our Privacy Statement & Cookie Policy  By continuing to browse our site you agree to our use of cookies, revised Privacy Policy and Terms of Use.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 145, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You can change your cookie settings through your browser.\", \"from\": 146, \"to\": 203, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Sports Scene  Copied  Liu Qingyi has been under bigger spotlights than ever in recent years, after becoming the first breaker from China to claim a medal at an international event during the Outbreak 2022 street dance competition, and winning the first-ever women's breaking gold medal at the 19th Asian Games in Hangzhou, east China's Zhejiang Province, in 2023.\", \"from\": 205, \"to\": 568, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 336, \"end\": 341, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"score\": 0.9576334245656097, \"rank\": 0.04421902755519679, \"text\": \"China\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\"}, {\"begin\": 518, \"end\": 526, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hangzhou\", \"score\": 0.9999999811523141, \"rank\": 1.5550932507629065e-08, \"text\": \"Hangzhou\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hangzhou\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hangzhou\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In an interview with CGTN Sports Scene's Shen Xiang, Liu talked about her Olympic preparation work, as well as her goals for the upcoming 2024 Paris Summer Olympics.\", \"from\": 570, \"to\": 735, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 591, \"end\": 595, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_Global_Television_Network\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 8.523602246322283e-24, \"text\": \"CGTN\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\", \"Q141683\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_Global_Television_Network\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_Global_Television_Network\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"For this period I have so many things to do because my coach, I have a lot of coaches, so they gave me a lot of advice,\\\" Liu said.\", \"from\": 737, \"to\": 868, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"So for me, I need to digest them and to transfer them to use by myself.\", \"from\": 870, \"to\": 942, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"So for now, I just want to put some new things and some old stuff together.\", \"from\": 943, \"to\": 1018, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Then I can find new feelings because I, I can only do the new things because it's very difficult and, I feel, maybe not stable.\", \"from\": 1019, \"to\": 1146, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"So for now, I will just try.\", \"from\": 1147, \"to\": 1175, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"If I crash, it's okay.\", \"from\": 1176, \"to\": 1198, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But as for the Olympics, I think that's the final stage,\\\" she added.\", \"from\": 1199, \"to\": 1267, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Breaking will make its debut as an Olympic sport at the Paris Games.\", \"from\": 1269, \"to\": 1337, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Liu, 18, says he wants to show \\\"Chinese style\\\" in her performance.\", \"from\": 1338, \"to\": 1404, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1370, \"end\": 1377, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"score\": 0.6256837037134854, \"rank\": 0.595680627143202, \"text\": \"Chinese\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I feel I am proud.\", \"from\": 1406, \"to\": 1425, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I just want to show some 'Chinese style' on the Olympic stage because breaking, maybe this is the first time (for it to be at) the Olympic Games,\\\" Liu said.\", \"from\": 1426, \"to\": 1582, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1452, \"end\": 1459, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"score\": 0.6256837037134854, \"rank\": 0.595680627143202, \"text\": \"Chinese\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Maybe this is the last time.\", \"from\": 1584, \"to\": 1613, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"So I will cherish this opportunity.\", \"from\": 1614, \"to\": 1649, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Thanks to our country for giving me this opportunity.\", \"from\": 1650, \"to\": 1703, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"So showing myself and showing 'Chinese style' on the Olympic stage will be my dream.\\\"\", \"from\": 1704, \"to\": 1789, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1735, \"end\": 1742, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"score\": 0.6256837037134854, \"rank\": 0.595680627143202, \"text\": \"Chinese\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The breaking events at the 2024 Paris Summer Olympics will take place from August 9-11.\", \"from\": 1791, \"to\": 1878, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"SITEMAP  EXPLORE MORE  DOWNLOAD OUR APP  Copyright \\u00c2\\u00a9 2024 CGTN.\\u00e4\\u00ba\\u00acICP\\u00e5\\u00a4\\u008720000184\\u00e5\\u008f\\u00b7  Disinformation report hotline: 010-85061466  SITEMAP  EXPLORE MORE  DOWNLOAD OUR APP  Copyright \\u00c2\\u00a9 2024 CGTN.\\u00e4\\u00ba\\u00acICP\\u00e5\\u00a4\\u008720000184\\u00e5\\u008f\\u00b7  Disinformation report hotline: 010-85061466\", \"from\": 1880, \"to\": 2140, \"entities\": []}]}"